{"tid":922162,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"俾你揀 你會揀記憶會慢慢淡忘 定 永遠都記得咁清楚？","createTime":"2018-11-30T06:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T17:39:46.000Z","uid":22455,"like":28,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3652ef25a035600a4ba100403cd2097a42e1d7","tid":922162,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"今日溫書諗起呢個問題 明明以前好識果個topic<br />\n格一排咩都唔記得哂 又要再溫過 好似初學者咁<br />\n好煩 好厭倦咁哂時間<br />\n但係相反<br />\n如果記憶唔會淡忘 就會一世記住<br />\n被ex扔低 被佢cut線 被分手既痛心經過<br />\n果種心痛既感覺真係痛撚到仆街<br />\n俾你揀 <br />\n慢慢淡忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c16fb9a742e8bff2f22bc90a0d3e7988c3c6e7","tid":922162,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"冇人講下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be840cd8eb59ea0b4cccd56434022f9582501ab","tid":922162,"uid":209532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63166baab7cc70c8c6dabe38358882422701c68","tid":922162,"uid":220421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"其實你淡忘吸取唔到教訓<br />\n記住自己衰咩<br />\n唔好再仆街多次仲好la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a335ba48d2bfde801637d852fbc099bea918f3","tid":922162,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e63166baab7cc70c8c6dabe38358882422701c68","tid":922162,"uid":220421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"其實你淡忘吸取唔到教訓<br />\n記住自己衰咩<br />\n唔好再仆街多次仲好la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"就係跌得太痛 唔想記住<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"6f13d74c60fd87e41bede6a5255df1adc3108067","tid":922162,"uid":22